/>\n加上支那死咗, 邊個出口啲衫褲鞋襪糧食畀美國?<br />\n<br />\n好心你就分析下先啦<br />\n下下都屈人係五毛小學雞<br />\n我唔鍾意支那, 我都唔想台灣俾人武統<br />\n但係個現實就係噉, 信不信由你"},{"pid":"9e92a7d19b6eff3cb777b846702acfd60d652b08","tid":577310,"uid":47359,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"10a8aea28dfcfbe1952d4d73f724239e71a8d0f3","tid":577310,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":48,"score":-47,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T15:54:06.000Z","msg":"班友都戇尻尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞依啲嘢習帝就有籍口出兵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T17:47:05.000Z","msg":"泛民激嬲中共論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e067d561b506040954c38e5150871b7e741a0ac8","tid":577310,"uid":2110,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"3d0691ee6a85a9d063430d97e125f835a2afd4b9","tid":577310,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":21,"score":-20,"quote":{"pid":"2863b161bc86d23ccab050a8fa9f6fbf715eaaaa","tid":577310,"uid":550,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"10a8aea28dfcfbe1952d4d73f724239e71a8d0f3","tid":577310,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":48,"score":-47,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T15:54:06.000Z","msg":"班友都戇尻尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞依啲嘢習帝就有籍口出兵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T17:29:56.000Z","msg":"雜總都話要喺2035年前解決台灣(問題)啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gi